Program: Great Lives
Title: Rudyard Kipling
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00mwm65
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 25 Aug 2017
Matthew Parris presents the biographical series in which his guests choose someone who has inspired their lives. John Major discusses the life of Rudyard Kipling, poet to the British Empire. They are joined by Kipling biographer Andrew Lycett.